# tests/test_allocation.py fails if the shares below drift from that
# derivation. Undisclosed gifts are NOT dropped: each year window's residual
# (announced tranche total minus disclosed dollars) is distributed across
# that window's undisclosed gifts in proportion to the recipient's pre-gift
# IRS 990 total revenue (ProPublica Nonprofit Explorer snapshot in
